15. Rae1 {[%cal Be5e6][%csl Be6]} -- ( { White shouldn't fear a capture on e5 since the plan has shifted towards creating a passed pawn on the e-file. White is already threatening the e6 advance. For example: } 15...Rb8 16.e6 Be8 17.Nxc6 Bxe3+ 18.Qxe3 { threatening the } { e7 advance. } )
